Package silverlib.img

Class Img

  • java.lang.Object
    • silverlib.img.Img
  • Direct Known Subclasses:
    Graph

    public class Img
extends java.lang.Object

    Simplified Image Class

    A class that stores an image as a collection of Color objects, and provides methods for examining, editing, dividing, and saving that image.
